ptguilds
Discworld creator help
ptguilds

.SH Name
.SI 5
ptguilds - Display playtesters by guild
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
ptguilds
ptguilds <guild>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command shows what Guilds the active playtesters belong too.  This
can be incredibly handy if you are looking for a playtester to kill,
main, and immolate and you want them to be a fat, juicy, over-weight 
and roast-ready Wizard.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> ptguilds

Playtester listing by Guild

Members of the Priests' Guild: Brighid, Chelan, Deo, Latazum, Primus and
Yukk.

Members of the Thieves' Guild: Chowmein, Emily, Harbringer, Oakenfold and
Scarlett.

...

> ptguilds /std/guilds/witch
Members of the Witches' Guild: Carpanag, Fizwort, Hufte, Myre, Rae, Satina
and Siel.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
playtesters
.EP

